The paper deals with combinatorial optimization problems related to graph and hypergraph coloring, matching, and independence number. These topics are typically studied in the areas of discrete mathematics (cs.DM), algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), computational geometry (cs.CG), graph theory (cs.GT), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
